Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼她要盯著我們看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們只是旅行 又沒做壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為那是她的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:18.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後就鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.91,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後呢 之後怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們就是要搭這架飛機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要搭飛機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我經常夢到自己是飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就是飛機
