Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛機已進入平穩飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燈熄了表示乘客可以離開座位走動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靜不下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真沒想到報瀨也是第一次搭飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然為媽媽送行過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但沒有實際搭過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結搭過很多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因為工作的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個要怎麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面有個遊戲的圖示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要點這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是蕎麥麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能用芹菜換你的雞蛋燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}綠茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右轉 往右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你別擠到我這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 為什麼只有我沒得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你在睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把這裡的「數據漫遊」關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把她叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虧你還睡得著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 全是英語耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要走哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要坐地鐵就走MRT的方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(690,650)}城市快捷運輸系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼會忘記兌換貨幣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且怎麼把身上的錢都換了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們後天早上就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不提前跟我說 我會忘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟我們在赤道附近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上次來的時候 我也有點想死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魚尾獅呢 魚尾獅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怪的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給點優惠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等會再來買啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是來個飯店就花這麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰叫你們買那些東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是為了轉機去費利曼圖才下機的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我們就待一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能隨意行動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雙人床
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預備 1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先出石頭 剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決定誰睡在小理身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理 你能睡在地上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正睡床上也會滾下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你訓練時就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我完全沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這才是問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出門前 先把貴重物品放進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日元 機票 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都在自己房間準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}30分鐘後在大廳集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我見過那個 是個泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:07.98,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※新加坡濱海灣金沙酒店，55層的泳池冠絕世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有想像中那麼讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我聽說很讓人失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們居然想失望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}排好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}擺什麼姿勢 擺什麼姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是烏龍茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}菜單上是這麼寫沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味噌拉麵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說沒有那東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但這是拉麵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為沒有味噌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這沒搞錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃不下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你嘴巴沒合上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我買到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}榴槤冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你居然還吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是甜點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向要不要嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得我會吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就給報瀨吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我早說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入境檢查時要出示護照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還帶在身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泳池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那邊 但只有這裡的住客才能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是個普通的泳池 就是景色很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 你進去過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前有次進去拍過照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說是性感泳裝寫真模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在笑話我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡有點像海上的十字路口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人們來到這裡 還會再前往世界各地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厲害什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後天 我們從這裡出發之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡的風景還會是這個樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管我們是去南極 還是回到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡每天還是會有船靠港
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}城裡還是會有許多人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上學 上班 和朋友們玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個人都繼續平時的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這話放到日本也適用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}學校今天依然有開課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在大概吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我們沒有見過 也不了解的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也有許許多多的人過著各式各樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天每天 從不間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然都是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過我能懂這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你隱瞞了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隱瞞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說不定會自己冒出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也不可能找成這樣都找不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這麼說也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有護照的話 別說出國了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連日本都回不去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 如果它一直不出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 我以前住在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼到了這裡還在便利商店上班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後天就要飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會有辦法 總會有辦法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辦法嘛…你想 肯定有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這…吐槽得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之先查查看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果遺失護照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到大使館重新辦理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最快也得花半天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天去還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是大使館星期日和節日沒開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星期日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}憑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明我們便利商店員 可是24小時全年無休
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這群臭公務員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能換搭晚兩三天的班機了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然到的時間會有點晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過還是能趕上發船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天去機場服務處問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要改…抵達日期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 觀測隊在紀律上是很嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會告訴我們不用來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會啦 事出有因嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傳個郵件問問佳苗小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要傳郵件說會遲到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這樣做比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是後天早上才走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有整整一天 明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也許它會自己突然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請你快快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.53,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魚尾獅…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真想殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 你們三個後天先去澳大利亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一個人也會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等趕上了 就會追上你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是沒趕上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就是回日本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}機票錢還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會去跟真理她們說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是我說不想變日期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我心裡也清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為不能按計劃走 心裡會有些煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弄丟護照的人是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該道歉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事實就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想給大家添麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是真像你說的 都去不了南極怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就追悔莫及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又沒有說不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是讓你們三個人先走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會追上去的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是四個人一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天跟佳苗小姐發郵件說明一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明你這麼為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我對這種事一直應付不來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然明白這種事其實很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我只要被別人關心就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該說是鬧彆扭呢 還是說看不透別人的本意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以連高中都不想上 想儘可能獨來獨往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結果我跟什麼人在一起 都會有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你不用在意 全都是我自己的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會的 我也有自己的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上高中後就一直全力釋放著別靠近我的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不擅長與人相處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.06,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你現在就是在關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了 我不喜歡被別人關心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨比任何人都想去南極吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把這點作為首要目標去考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來 我也會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬧鐘沒響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這邊 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們怎麼自己跑出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽說你是身體不適才睡覺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月去問機票能不能改了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這件事就不用你們操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經說好了 你們三個先去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒聽過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之後已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別講傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼那麼意氣用事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是誰意氣用事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種票要一個多月後才有位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為本來就是特價機票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看 我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之你們三個明天先去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一個人去補辦護照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改簽！推延兩天！機票！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(640,650)}Change, later two days, air
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想改簽！四個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(640,650)}Please change, four person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 為什麼要意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意氣用事有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}固執 被人取笑 鬧得不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我依然很意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我沒有做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你不想我關心 就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不想當 別人說不用關心 就真不關心的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不想當 別人叫他先走 就真走了的無情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說好四個人一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不想當出爾反爾的窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們四個人一起走 這就是首要目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我覺得不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是商務艙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用做到這種地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有別的空位 也只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弄丟就麻煩了 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是100萬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在得意些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有得意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 也有點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不喜歡被別人擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之現在得四個人一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天大家一起去大使館…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鞋帶鬆了 幫我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不找個地方裝 很容易掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海南雞飯 海南雞飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 海南雞飯和咖椰烤吐司來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 哇 看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你隱瞞了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隱瞞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩位趕快開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨和日向的榴槤秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要吃這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就放過你們了 還不快感謝我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是 你知道我們多擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是商務艙票也退票了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出發日還是明天不變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還剛好分成了四塊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猜拳輸的一方吃如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這哪裡算什麼水果之王了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過習慣了 可能還挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Comment: 0,0:21:59.03,0:21:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:19.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:30.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:36.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:47.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:58.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.28,0:23:09.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:15.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:20.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:19.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:30.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:36.42,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:47.37,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:58.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.28,0:23:09.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:15.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:20.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
